IConcept:DISEASE

From ES MetaNet Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search
SourceID 17
Government Definition a disordered or incorrectly functioning organ, part, structure, or system of the body resulting from the effect of genetic or developmental errors, infection, poisons, nutritional deficiency or imbalance, toxicity, or unfavorable environmental factors; illness; sickness; ailment
Comments (Internal)
Status white
Owner GOV
